Package: monographaR
Version: 1.3.0
Date: 2024-01-10
Title: Taxonomic Monographs Tools
Author: Marcelo Reginato
Maintainer: Marcelo Reginato <reginatobio@yahoo.com.br>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: knitr
Imports: circular, png, raster, rmarkdown, rnaturalearth, rpart, sf, sp, terra
Description: Contains functions intended to facilitate the production of plant taxonomic monographs. The package includes functions to convert tables into taxonomic descriptions, lists of collectors, examined specimens, dichotomous keys, and can generate a monograph skeleton. Additionally, wrapper functions to batch the production of phenology charts and distributional and diversity maps are also available. 
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL (>= 2)

